  Locus:
    Page: 30
    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Awakening/Awareness
---
Our original ... Nature is, in highest truth, devoid of any atom of
objectivity. It is void, omnipresent, silent, pure; it is glorious and
mysterious peaceful joy -- and that is all. Enter deeply into it by awakening
yourself.
